summaries.short: Season One Finale. A turkey seeks vengeance on Thanksgiving; rat teens discover joys and horrors as they venture out of the sewer.
summaries.full: Season One Finale. After his wife is taken from him, a turkey seeks revenge on the mayor during the Thanksgiving parade. Two rat teens venture out of the sewer and discover the joys and horrors of life above ground.

summaries.short: A group of roaches bands together when an exterminator threatens their lives; conjoined seagulls struggle to live as one.
summaries.full: When an exterminator puts a roach town in crisis, the survivors band together to travel to the world outside of their wall and guarantee the survival of their species. A group of seagulls, stuck together by a piece of litter, struggle to live their lives as one.

summaries.short: The conclusion of a group of squirrels' treacherous trek out of their collapsed tree home; a queen ant learns what her colony thinks of her.
summaries.full: The thrilling conclusion of squirrels Phil, Mike and April's treacherous journey out of their collapsed tree home; a queen ant reunites with an old friend and learns what her colony really thinks of her.

summaries.short: Squirrel brothers face their own anxieties while preparing for their mom's remarriage.
summaries.full: With New York City quarantined and in disarray, squirrels Mike and Phil prepare for their mother's remarriage. As Mike tries to impress a female guest, Phil plots to stop the wedding, squaring off with his soon-to-be little brother, the attention-hog Mason.

summaries.short: Young squirrel brothers test their survival skills on a journey to escape their overturned tree home.
summaries.full: After their home collapses, two young squirrel brothers find their survival skills tested on a journey through a tree trunk towards freedom, meeting rodent friends and foes along the way. A snake and her mouse prey face off; puppies at a pet store settle a turf war.
